description:
This topic presents the location and expansion of the other water areas in Dresden as of August 2021. These water areas are not waters within the meaning of the Water Act.   The following factual information is offered on the individual water surfaces: Information on the creator of the individual area, e.g. Environmental Agency or a specific company (source); Information on the basis on which situation and extent were determined, e.g. surveying, orthographic, TK (GRUNDLAGE); Name (GEWNA, if available); unique number (GEWNR); Location description (note, if available);
Order (order, here:
no waters and ORND_KZ, here:
10);
Area in m² (FLAECHE) as well as change dates.

